data.description: Needing lots of space for your family? You may want to check out this beautiful home. Located near just about everything Alma has to offer is this large brick home.  Once you walk into the home your greeted with a very spacious living room, large wood burning fireplace and a formal dining area off the kitchen. There is a welcoming dining/breakfast bar in the kitchen, lots of kitchen cabinets and countertop space. This will be the home you invite your whole family to for holiday gatherings.  Also, a bonus room right of the kitchen to turn into whatever you like, extra bedroom, workout room, office or storage. Bedrooms are large, master bath has room to add double sinks. Walk-In closet in main bedroom. Covered front porch to enjoy your morning coffee. Back yard has wood privacy fence for your convenience. With a little TLC your personal touches to this house you can make this into your dream home.
